#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&klickety; is an adaptation of the Clickomania game. The rules are "
#| "similar to those of the Same game: your goal is to clear the board by "
#| "clicking on groups to destroy them. The overall aim is to get the lowest "
#| "score possible. It will provide entertainment for all abilities, but a "
#| "challenge in logical thought if you want to get a really low score."
msgid ""
"&klickety; is an adaptation of the <application>Clickomania</application> "
"game. The rules are similar to those of the <literal>Same</literal> game: "
"your goal is to clear the board by clicking on groups to destroy them. The "
"overall aim is to get the lowest score possible. It will provide "
"entertainment for all abilities, but a challenge in logical thought if you "
"want to get a really low score."
msgstr ""
"&klickety; je adaptacija Clickomania igre. Pravila su slična sa onim od Iste "
"igre, vas cilj je da očistite tablu klikom na grupe da ih uništite. Sve u "
"svemu svrha je da dobijete što manji broj poena moguće. To će vam "
"obezbjediti zabavu za sve sposobnosti, ali i izazov u logičnom razmišljanju "
"ako želite da postavite mali rezultat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Objektiv:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clear the game board of all the colored blocks in the least possible time."
msgstr "Očistiti tablu igre od svih obojenih kocki u što manje vremena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the program you will get a screen that looks something like "
"the screenshot in the previous section. The idea of the game is to remove "
"blocks, which you do by clicking on them."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete program dobiti ćete zaslon koji izgleda kao zaslon iz "
"prethodnog odjeljka. Ideja igre je da pomijerite kocke, što uradite klikom "
"na njima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, you can only remove a block if it is adjacent to one or more other "
"blocks of the same color on one or more of its sides. Diagonal connections "
"do not count. You get a random board every time you start a new game."
msgstr ""
"Međutim, možete pomijetiri kocku ako je susjedna uz jednu ili vise drugih "
"kocki istih boja na jednoj ili više svojih strana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a block which is connected as described, it will disappear. "
"Any adjacent blocks of the same color will also disappear, along with all of "
"the same color adjacent to <emphasis>them</emphasis>, and so on. Any blocks "
"above them drop down to fill the gaps left by the disappeared pieces. If you "
"clear an entire column, all the columns to the right move across to fill the "
"gap."
msgstr ""
"Ako kliknete na kocku koja je spojena, kao što je opisano, ona će nestati. "
"Sve susjedne kocke istih boje će također nestati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game ends when there are no blocks adjacent to other blocks of the same "
"colour."
msgstr "Igra završava kada nema vise kocki susjedne drugim kockama istih boja."

