#, no-c-format
msgid "A quick explanation of the parts of the game screen."
msgstr "Kratko objašnjenje djelova zaslona igre."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Screen"
msgstr "Zaslon igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Game screen is in the center of the screen and is the largest section of "
"the window."
msgstr "Zaslon igre je u centru zaslona i zauzima najveći dio prozora."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Statusna traka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Status bar is located at the bottom of the screen. It displays how many "
"pieces are left currently and the game timer, which keeps track of the "
"elapsed time from the start of the game until the game is finished."
msgstr ""
"Statusna traka se nalazi na dnu zaslona. Pokazuje koliko je dijelova ostalo "
"i vrijeme igre, koje prati proteklo vrijeme od početka igre dok se igra ne "
"završi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "The KSame Mode"
msgstr "KSame Način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "&klickety; provides a &ksame; scoring mode."
msgstr "&klickety; obezbjeđuje &ksame; način pogodaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "The score is calculated as follows:"
msgstr "Rezultat se izračunava na sljedeći način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subtract 2 from the number of marbles erased, and square the result."
msgstr "Oduzmi 2 od broja izbrisanih klikera, i kvadrirajte rezultat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As an example, if you erase 7 balls, then you get 25 points (7 minus 2 = "
#| "5. 5 squared is 25 points).If you erase 8 balls, then you get 36 points "
#| "(8 minus 2 = 6. 6 squared is 36 points."
msgid ""
"As an example, if you erase 7 balls, then you get 25 points (7 minus 2 = 5, "
"5 squared is 25 points). If you erase 8 balls, then you get 36 points (8 "
"minus 2 = 6, 6 squared is 36 points)."
msgstr ""
"Kao primjer, ako obrišete 7 lopti, onda dobijate 25 poena (7 minus 2 = 5. 5 "
"kvadrirano je 25 poena). Ako obrišete 8 lopti, onda dobijate 36 poena (8 "
"minus 2 = 6. 6 kvadrirano je 36 poena)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Get as many of the same pieces as you can, and then erase them in one click. "
"That way you will get a higher score. The game is over when there are no "
"pieces that can be erased."
msgstr "Uzmi što više dijelova, onda ih izbrisati u jednom kliku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score will then be decreased according to the number of remaining "
"pieces. If you erase all pieces 1,000 bonus points will be added to the "
"final score."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat će se smanjiti u skladu sa brojem preostalih dijelova. Ako obrišete "
"sve dijelove 1,000 bonus poena će biti dodani na finalnom rezultatu."

