#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim promijeniti izgled igre. Mogu li?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the way &klickety; looks use the menubar to open the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">configuration utility</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da. Da bi promijenili izgled &klickety; koristite menubar da bi otvorili "
"<link linkend=\"configuration\">configuration utility</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Mogu li koristiti tastaturu za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not feature a keyboard play mode yet."
msgstr "Ne. Ova igra ne sadrži način za igranje na nastaturi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to start the game in KSame mode?"
msgstr "Kako početi igru na KSame način?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can launch &klickety; with command <userinput>klickety --KSameMode</"
"userinput> or &ksame; menu entry in K menu."
msgstr ""
"Možete lansirati &klickety; sa komandom <userinput>klickety --KSameMode</"
"userinput> ili &ksame; menu ulazak u K meni."

